      <p style="text-align:center;margin-left:0.01in;margin-right:0.04in;text-indent:-0.01in"><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:18pt">RULING ON COSTS  </span></p>
      <p style="text-align:center;margin-left:0.01in;margin-right:0.04in;text-indent:-0.01in"><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:18pt">(Made on written submissions) </span></p>
      <p style="text-align:center;margin-left:2.16in;margin-right:2.19in;text-indent:-0.01in">............................. </p>
      <p style="text-align:center;margin-left:2.16in;margin-right:2.2in;text-indent:-0.01in">MR JUSTICE MOSTYN </p>
      <p style="margin-left:-0.01in;margin-right:0.03in;text-indent:0in">This judgment was delivered in private.   The judge has given leave for this version of the judgment to be published on condition that (irrespective of what is contained in the judgment) in any published version of the judgment the anonymity of the children and members of their family must be strictly preserved.   All persons, including representatives of the media, must ensure that this condition is strictly complied with.   Failure to do so will be a contempt of court. </p>
      <p style="text-align:left;margin-left:0in;margin-right:0in;text-indent:0in"><span style="font-weight:bold;text-decoration-line:underline;text-decoration-style:solid;font-size:8pt">MR JUSTICE MOSTYN</span><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:8pt"/><marker name="tab"/><span style="font-size:8pt">LM v DM </span></p>
      <p style="text-align:left;margin-left:0.07in;margin-right:0in;text-indent:-0.01in"><span style="font-weight:bold;text-decoration-line:underline;text-decoration-style:solid;font-size:8pt">Approved Judgment</span></p>
